	   <tr><td colspan=2>You bring up a couple issues that I'm concerned with.&nbsp;&nbsp;See, I play EQ for one reason and one reason alone: to play.  I'm not overly concerned with xyz uber weapon.  I'm not going to start a smacktalk fest because it's my only social outlet (read some guild bulletin boards and you'll see what I mean).  I am mainly looking to find a set of people that I can play with on a somewhat regular basis.  We can become familiar with each other's playing styles, and maximize our effectiveness.  If we do a crawl we can actually talk about 'what went wrong' when we get rolled on, as opposed to half the group saying "let's go back to Overthere or LoIO, it's so much easier".  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
